title.narrative: Can Tho Urban Development and Resilience

description.narrative: The Project Development Objective is to reduce flood risk in the urban core area, improve connectivity between the city center and the new low risk urban growth areas, and enhance the capacity of city authorities to manage disaster risk in Can Tho City.
